kw.name: Testsuite Setup
kw.doc: This testsuite_setup defines the ``Testsuite Setup`` which is used to loads the RobotFramework AIO configuration, checks the version of RobotFramework AIO, and logs out the basic information of the robot run.
kw.msg: Set suite metadata 'project' to value 'RobotFramework Testsuites'.
Set suite metadata 'tester' to value 'Queckenstedt Holger (XC-CT/ECA3)'.
Set suite metadata 'testtool' to value 'Robot Framework 4.1.3 (Python 3.9.16 on win32)'.
${teststring_common} = I am the common teststring valid for all variants and all test benches
${teststring_bench} = I am the teststring containing the default value for all test benches
${teststring_variant} = I am the 'variant1' configuration of tsm-test

${CONFIG} = {'WelcomeString': 'Hello... Robot Framework is running now!', 'Maximum_version': '1.0.0', 'Minimum_version': '0.6.0', 'Project': 'RobotFramework Testsuites', 'TargetName': 'Device_01', 'params': {}}
Robot Framework AIO version check passed!
